show.title: The Price Of Pride

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/hSySnF
show.description:
Once mocked as a poor mechanic, humiliated by in-laws, and abandoned by his own family—he vanished without a trace.
Years later, he returns—not as the man they scorned, but as the billionaire who’ll bring their empire to its knees. When power shifts, who will bow first—the tycoons blinded by pride or the man they once called worthless? Watch now.
